<section id="tribute-info">
<h3 id="headline">Here's a time line of Polprawee's life:</h3>
<ul>
<li><strong>1977</strong> - Born in Sukothai province, Thailand</li>
<li>
<strong>1986 - 1991</strong> - Participated in elementary school football competitions in Prachuap Khiri Khan Province.
</li>
<li>
<strong>1992</strong> - Participated in the U16 football competition in Phetchaburi province.
</li>
<li>
<strong>1993 - 1994</strong> <br> - Gold medal in the U18 football competition in Phetchaburi province.<br> - Silver medal in student football competition. Selection of educational district 5th representative.<br> - Bronze medal in the national youth football competition. Selection of district 7th representative.<br> - Participated in national football competition. Selection of district 7th representative.
</li>
<li>
<strong>2017</strong> - FA Thailand Introductory Course.
</li>
<li>
<strong>2018</strong> - Football coach U8 Mossa academy.
</li>
</ul>
<h3>
